data.title: Brittany Murphy Movies and Shows
data.meta_description: Learn about Brittany Murphy on Apple TV. Browse shows and movies that feature Brittany Murphy including Clueless, Little Black Book, and more.
data.text:
Give Him the Chair

Frasier learns that sentiment is more important than style after he accidentally loses his father's old armchair.

First Dates

Tamera decides to go with a date to the school dance, breaking a promise to Tia as they had both agreed to stay home unless they both had dates.

Cheater, Cheater

Tia makes the honor roll at school, Tamera overhears Ray and Lisa discussing their kids and school and decides to make Ray proud of her by getting an A on her history test.

The Birthday

It's the twins birthday and Lisa gets them a present they love until they see Ray's. His is a limo trip to Chicago. Excited, the twins forget about Lisa and get ready for Chicago
